reviews.review_text: better I think this is an improvement to the other SBD of this show. It's the complete show and it just sounds better. The speed is correct on this one. I'm thinking the bass is lacking a little in comparison to the other version, I guess.. I don't know, but overall the fidelity is more like a normal recording of a show. I'm hoping the 3/10/85 and 3/12/85 soundboards will surface one day. That would be so nice. Thanks again for this show!
Great show Thanks for upping it.
- Not a bad show; not the greatest sound quality; definitely not the worst.
